OL,6,FHow long is the disruption expected to
OL,7,Flast?
OL,9,FThe London Fire Brigade said the fire
OL,10,Fat the electrical substation is under
OL,11,Fcontrol, but a Heathrow spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid they "still do not have clarity
OL,13,Fon when power may be reliably
OL,14,Frestored."
OL,16,F"We expect significant disruption over
OL,17,Fthe coming days and passengers should
OL,18,Fnot travel to the airport under any
OL,19,Fcircumstances until the airport
OL,20,Freopens," they added.
