OL,4,Crights if my flight is disrupted?
OL,6,FRory Boland said: "If you accept a
OL,7,Frefund, be aware that your airline
OL,8,Fwill have no further duty of care to
OL,9,Fyou and you'll need to make your own
OL,10,Farrangements."
OL,12,F"It's also worth checking the terms of
OL,13,Fyour travel insurance to see if you
OL,14,Fare able to recoup any other expenses
OL,15,Fyou may have incurred as a result of
OL,16,Fthis incident, such as car hire or
OL,17,Fairport parking fees."
