OL,3,CHeathrow power outage: What are my
OL,4,Crights if my flight is disrupted?
OL,6,FAccording to the Civil Aviation
OL,7,FAuthority (CAA), an airline must
OL,8,Fprovide a reasonable amount of food
OL,9,Fand drink in the case of a
OL,10,F"significant delay".
OL,12,FCan I claim compensation?
OL,14,FAirlines are required to pay
OL,15,Fcompensation if flights arrive more
OL,16,Fthan three hours late, but only when
OL,17,Fit is deemed to be within their
OL,18,Fcontrol, such as a fault with the
OL,19,Faircraft or pilot sickness.
